{"tid":2132378,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"《扛麥翁》","createTime":"2020-07-30T10:49:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T11:04:35.000Z","uid":21255,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0cfd0c0f99d8f17bc8a3c54543550a95526ddcc0","tid":2132378,"uid":21255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T10:49:32.000Z","msg":"岳飛字鵬舉諮善扛，神力無雙 ，公亦以此自矜。嘗挽弓於家圃，有扛麥翁釋擔而立，睨之，久而不去。見其挽弓二三百斤，但微頷之。<br />\n岳飛問曰：&rdquo;汝亦知扛乎？吾力不亦神乎？&rdquo;翁曰：&rdquo;無他， 唯換肩爾。&rdquo;岳飛忿然曰：&rdquo;爾安敢輕吾力！&rdquo;翁曰：&rdquo;以我扛麥知之。&rdquo;乃取二百斤麥置於籮，以擔搭其肩，徐走十里山路之，自山腳入，而肩不換。因曰：&rdquo;我亦無他，唯不換肩。&rdquo;岳飛笑而遣之。"},{"pid":"edaddab3430340d9b47821ef7d507bb58090e169","tid":2132378,"uid":21255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T10:51:20.000Z","msg":"刁粽 字維尼 陝西富平人也<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2131956\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2131956</a>"},{"pid":"d2e432f130f169ae8680400215e40785d6fee8a1","tid":2132378,"uid":21255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T11:04:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}